            </div><p>My goal with this project is to build a fully open-source <a href="https://meshtastic.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Meshtastic</a>/<a href="https://meshcore.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Meshcore</a> compatible client that is more &ldquo;rugged&rdquo; than what is currently available on the market. If there is enough interest, I will consider manufacturing a few and getting CE etc. certification done. If you are interested, please join the mailing list below.</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>